explanation: This solution uses dynamic programming to track the state of individuals (represented by bitmasks) and the current stage. For each state, it tries to transport a group of people and updates the stage and time accordingly. It also considers the return trip for one person if not all individuals are transported. The solution aims to find the minimum total time required to transport all individuals.

